rows.label: tlk43400441_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Don't see a lot of Superbians
on the streets of Invidia, do you?

rows.label: tlk43400441_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My husband's an Invidian. He
works as a mercenary.

rows.label: tlk43400441_01_msg0003
rows.name:
My dad's in the mercenary business
too, so that's how we originally met...

rows.label: tlk43400441_01_msg0004
rows.name: He tells me about his fights every day.

rows.label: tlk43400441_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Some enemies can only defend in
certain directions. To the front only, or
the front and sides...

rows.label: tlk43400441_01_msg0006
rows.name:
His stories get a bit bloody, but I've got
a strong stomach, so we get on well.
